{"tid":2427863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉：收到帖文指劉利群是泛民內奸，其丈夫是泛民策劃首腦","createTime":"2021-03-01T06:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T12:57:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"36703954bf847c5ade334e15943e5c3da5e1f8fe","tid":2427863,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】食環署前署長劉利群日前獲晉升為食衞局常任秘書長後被抨擊，曾任政務官的新民黨主席葉劉淑儀質疑有人藉「愛國者治港」造文章。 <br />\n<br />\n新民黨主席葉劉淑儀：「國安法推出後，支持國安法的標語立即被清除，據我了解其實並非食環署工作，真的與食環署無關，是負責交通、運輸部門。收到帖文指劉利群是泛民內奸，其丈夫是泛民策劃首腦，我說有沒有弄錯？一個署長可以做內奸？一個社工是這般厲害？如果屬實，他們早已被捕，這些真的太誇張至無知。」"},{"pid":"8723c2ac1cd65f9e1498352a557ced9df6bb514a","tid":2427863,"uid":2054,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:14:35.000Z","msg":"係你啦 過黎啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2018/12/31/world/00china-cultrev-1/merlin_148624668_0f6bf3de-d53a-4c79-96dc-d04ae6bf4973-master1050.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F12%2F31%2Fworld%2F00china-cultrev-1%2Fmerlin_148624668_0f6bf3de-d53a-4c79-96dc-d04ae6bf4973-master1050.jpg&h=56b2f206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.hk.epochtimes.com//uploads/pictures/32355/content_cultural-revolution.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.hk.epochtimes.com%2F%2Fuploads%2Fpictures%2F32355%2Fcontent_cultural-revolution.jpg&h=9c15071e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a44f25661d87bef84132651d47b1c7656756d006","tid":2427863,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:15:28.000Z","msg":"！葉劉你反抗？犯法呀"},{"pid":"8d8daae00e73a7e1071864a4cca585223c7665f8","tid":2427863,"uid":59976,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">支持香港文革</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img